# Google AI API Key for Gemini
#
# REQUIRED: This key is necessary for the AI doodle guessing functionality
#
# How to get your API key:
# 1. Visit https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Create API Key" button
# 4. Copy the generated key (it will start with "AIza...")
#
# For local development:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder below with your actual API key
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control!
#
# For Vercel deployment:
# 1. Add this as an environment variable in Vercel Dashboard
# 2. Go to Project Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add GOOGLE_GENAI_API_KEY with your key
# 4. See VERCEL_SETUP.md for detailed instructions
#
GOOGLE_GENAI_API_KEY=AIzaSyD07J_mFilOXzPDL69TK3297v5qLhQdHB8

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# - The .env.local file is gitignored and will NOT be committed
# - NEVER commit API keys to version control
# - Each developer needs their own .env.local file
# - Production keys should only be in Vercel environment variables
